===========================================
Protocol Standards and Dependencies
===========================================

This software implements the following open protocol standards:

Stratum Protocol:
- Stratum V1 follows the de facto Bitcoin mining protocol standard
- Stratum V2 implementation references the Stratum V2 Specification
  (https://github.com/stratum-mining/sv2-spec)

Bitcoin Protocol:
- Block template handling follows BIP 22/23 (getblocktemplate)
- Transaction encoding follows Bitcoin Core specifications
- SHA256d hashing per the Bitcoin whitepaper

ZMQ Implementation:
- Uses go-zeromq/zmq4 (https://github.com/go-zeromq/zmq4)
  Licensed under: BSD-3-Clause License

Cryptographic Protocols:
- Noise Protocol Framework (https://noiseprotocol.org/) - Public Domain specification
- Used for Stratum V2 encrypted channel establishment

See THIRD_PARTY_LICENSES.txt for complete list of dependencies and their licenses.

